name: Passport of my future country
description: This document will be official when i, Hafırat, achieve my life goal and found my own, perfect country. There will be no rulers, no leaders, no bullies, no dictators. Just people minding their own business. The owners of this document will be welcome and become citizen. There is no name or a flag yet. But may be there won’t be any. If you think that you may need a new country, don’t hesitate and buy this document. Think like it’s an insurance for future.
